csAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ezl1665702724946.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ezl1665702724946.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ezl1665702724946.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ezl1665702724946\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      stepsize\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the number of entries are selected in one step of a stepped hitlist.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ezl1665702724946__topic_d51269e1_d51270e1_d51271e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ezl1665702724946__p_d51272e1_d51273e1_d51274e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$LDP_PARAMS = stepsize:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ezl1665702724946__section_uxt_k2g_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d348738e63\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ezl1665702724946__p_d51278e1_d51279e1_d51280e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>—number of entries in step;\n            if not specified, defaults to <code class=\"ph codeph\">10</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ezl1665702724946__section_fyv_l2g_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d348738e77\">Example: stepsize</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ezl1665702724946__pre_dyj_n2g_jcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">USYS$LDP_PARAMS = stepsize:25</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gwm1665702661923.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Stepped Hitlists</a><p>Uniface uses the Select request to create a partially built hitlist called a stepped hitlist. This mechanism ensures that a limited number of occurrences are fetched from the database, even though a large number of occurrences match the retrieve profile entered by the user.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527402\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527402\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "stepsize Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 12, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 stepsize Set the number of entries are selected in one step of a stepped hitlist. USYS$LDP_PARAMS = stepsize: Number Arguments Number —number of entries in step; if not specified, defaults to 10 . Example: stepsize USYS$LDP_PARAMS = stepsize:25 Copy Related Links Stepped Hitlists Uniface uses the Select request to create a partially built hitlist called a stepped hitlist. This mechanism ensures that a limited number of occurrences are fetched from the database, even though a large number of occurrences match the retrieve profile entered by the user. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}